article.headline: Jackson scores 19 as South Dakota State beats Southern Miss 101-76
article.description: — Jaden Jackson scored 19 points as South Dakota State beat Southern Miss 101-76 on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Jackson scores 19 as South Dakota State beats Southern Miss 101-76
article.story: BROOKINGS, S.D. -- — Jaden Jackson scored 19 points as South Dakota State beat Southern Miss 101-76 on Wednesday night. Jackson had 10 rebounds for the Jackrabbits (4-1). Oscar Cluff scored 16 points while shooting 7 of 7 from the field and added nine rebounds. Kalen Garry shot 3 for 8 (1 for 5 from 3-point range) and 7 of 7 from the free-throw line to finish with 14 points. The Golden Eagles (2-2) were led by Neftali Alvarez, who posted 13 points. Christian Watson added 12 points and two steals for Southern Miss. Denijay Harris also had 11 points and 12 rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
